Welcome to this beautiful 3860 sq/ft ranch-style home that exudes both comfort and functionality. Nestled on a private street, this residence boasts 5 spacious bedrooms, each accompanied by its own walk-in closet, a large open office, 4 bathrooms, triple garage, fenced yard, deck, concrete patio, boat or camper parking, and upper and lower laundry.
The main level of the home features an open concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Cherry cabinets are found throughout the kitchen and bathrooms and a large walk-in pantry provides the kitchen additional storage. The living room is equipped with a gas fireplace and access to the deck and backyard, but the standout feature is the master bedroom. This room boasts a trey ceiling, large walk-in closet, and a bathroom containing both a walk-in shower and soaker tub.
The lower level has an open family room with a gas fireplace, full bar, and breakfast nook. This area also hosts additional storage in the wide hallways going to each of the spacious bedrooms. These bedrooms have ample room for a growing household, each with its own walk-in closet.

The exterior has a fully fenced yard with landscaping and perennials throughout. It also offers plenty of locations to relax no matter the time of day with its concrete patio, front porch, and rear deck. If you are looking to get outdoors on the weekend, the side yard contains a parking area for a boat and has a 30-amp outlet for a RV or Camper.
